  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b8e\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sabugaskanda oil refinery workers protest",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Employees of the Sabugaskanda oil refinery staged a protest on Tuesday (28) demanding that the Sabugaskanda refinery continue to supply crude oil and protesting against the handing over of filling stations to foreign companies.",
        "The demonstration, which took place during their lunch break, took place in front of the main entrance of the Sappugaskanda oil refinery.",
        "Speaking at the event, Shantha Vettaketiya, President of the Oil Refinery Executive Officers' Association, said:",
        "\"It has been reported that many oil filling stations are to be handed over to the private sector. We do not yet know what its content is. We will look into this and take the next steps, \u201dhe said.",
        "Saminda Pathirana, vice-president of the Sri Lanka Independent Employees' Union, said that supplying crude oil to the refinery would help alleviate the country's fuel shortage, which is worsening today, and provide fuel for essential services."
      ],
